 mother said - you know we were getting the things - all us things together, now she said, now we just want - some cotton. You know, some - and - and I thought - and - a needle, but I said, cotton and - and - is that to be strong - I said, cotton, what fo
r
? I said, they nev - they never - sew me up with - she said it went in there and it 'll come out there. She said, and you've had the sweet, you'll have to have the bitters. And I mean they used to be hard, confinements did then. Had terrible pain, but I'd
 - I'd rather have the pain than have any ana}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11809149\charrsid5456321 esthe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 
tic, I think you shouldn't have anything like that when you're having your baby naturally.
