\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Yes, she was a nurse, she came. Oh she didn't do anything in the house, oh no. Took me temperature an
