\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 No. Oh now - no, he wasn't like my father, my father were - he - he believed in - reading, you know, like men - he belie
