\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5909703 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Did he ever tell them stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 
