\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Oh yes, yes, he - oh he'd take them out, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5909703 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 But he would never look after them while you were out?
