Oh no, I always put them to bed, while they got old enough, well - then - when our Alfred got about - seven, our youngest, me youngest was seven, well he - he - he went - go to bed 
- with the big one, but they never slept together. They had two wood beds, yes, single beds. Same as me and my husband, we had - twin beds.
