reakfast like - of course I used to - slip home, you know, and give 'em - have their breakfast, I used to have it all ready and just have to make the tea. But you see, when they got - as I put them out they had it - you see, there was no breakfast to make
. They had it where they were - I paid for them, I paid - good money for them mind.
