\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5909703 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 How did you go on for your breakfast, did you used to go home and have it or did you have it before you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 
Oh - I - well I ate it before I went out at six o'clock and I used to make do while dinnertime, and then when I got home I'd make a dinner at night for 'em, and - have an
ything, he'd just have to put a light to potatoes, I used to cook the meat and - he'd have to just warm it you know, or whatever we had and - and I'd come home and I'd get a - a slice of bread and butter and I'd eat that and I wouldn't have any dinner. Ju
st to - I - oh there were plenty but I wouldn't have no dinner. And - and the doctor's come many a time and - and - and my husband said, look, that's her dinner. And he - he - and he did, but I've never had margarine in me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5909703 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Was that because you were short of money, you couldn't afford to buy food for all of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Well I could yes, but I hadn't time to eat it and look after me children. And look after me husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5909703 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 You used to prepare the night before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Yes. I used to get the meat in as
 I were coming home, it used to be fresh from the Co-op, used to get it for me and he used to cook it, and sometime it'd be a little roast, you know, 'cos it isn't like it now, you can't get roasts now, I never have a roast now, I never have hardly any ho
t dinners. I - I get potatoes and I'll boil two and it's quite enough for me sometime and I don't want no more. I can live on a meal a day me.
