\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3691612 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Oh yes, they've - they've been - they've sung, but - you know in our home, and - my youngest boy was made a - a r
ecord at - Morecambe, you know, in one of them booths and it - oh it were lovely. Amongst my Souvenirs, oh it was - she said to me, put it on once and she said, who's that man? I said - I said, it's our Edward. Used to laugh. Well he had it and he give it
 to his son, and do you know they - they have - have loads of fun with it you know and that. Singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5909703 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971545\charrsid5456321 Did you ever make music together, the four of you?
